quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,33,"Tɩ bãmb sẽn tʋmã wẽng puk ne bãmba, tɩ gũbg bãmb bũmb ning bãmb sẽn da yɩ n yaandẽ wã."
  45,34,"Tɩ b yeele: "rũndã D yĩmda yãmb yell wala yãmb sẽn yĩm y ra-kãngã segbã, la y gãag zĩig yaa Bugmẽ, y pa tar sõngd buudu"."
  45,35,"Yaa woto tɩ bala yãmb rɩka Wẽnd Aaya-rãmbã ne yaalgo, tɩ Dũni vɩɩmã belg yãmba, rẽnd rũndã b pa na n yiis yãmb a pʋgẽ ye, b pa na n leb yaaf-b ye."
  45,36,"Rẽnd Pẽgr tiugung be ne Wẽnde, saas la tẽng Naabã, bõn-naands Naabã."
  45,37,"La Yẽ n so waoog-m-menga, saasẽ la tẽnga, la Yẽ la ɑ Wind n yaa bʋʋd Mita."
  46,1,"Hɑɑ miim"
  46,2,"Gafã sigbã yii Wẽnd nengẽ sẽn yaa wilb Naabã n yaa bʋʋd Mitã."
  46,3,"Tõnd pa naan saasã la Tẽngã la bũmb nins sẽn be b yiibã sʋka, rẽnda ne sɩd la wakat sẽn tar tεka, la neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã yaa balldba n yi bũmb ning b sẽn bugsd-bã."
  46,4,"Yeele: "kõ-y maam kibar ne bũmb ning yãmb sẽn tũud tɩ pa yɩ ne Wẽndã, wilg-y maam bõe la b naan tẽn-gãngã zugu, bɩ b tara lagem-n-taar saasẽ wã? Wa-y ne gaf sẽn yi bãmb nengẽ n reng yãoã taoore (Alkʋrãanã), ma bãngr vũun tɩ y sã n yaa sɩd-rãmba"."
  46,5,"La ãnd meneng n yɩɩd neb sẽn boond zẽng sẽn pa Wẽnde, neb nins sẽn pa na n sak a yĩng hal n tɩ tãag yikrã raare, lɑ b Rʋbsã rɑyɩɩme n yaa yam yaal-yaal rãmbɑ, n pɑ mi bãmb tũudmã ye."